{"bio":null,"bio_l":"如果神明做了噩梦，那一定是祸乱之源带来的。被称为阿特洛波斯的祸乱之源诞生自夜之女神妮塔莎午夜的恐惧。永生的女神在漫长的时间中孕育了过强的恐惧，已经无法用睡眠抑制，于是，祸乱之源在不断蚕食女神的不朽之身后，从她的躯体中逃脱了，他雾状的身形源自女神墨色的鲜血。他的存在就是恐惧本身。听见他声音的凡人会感觉他们心中最阴暗的秘密在耳边低语。他呼唤着所有英雄内心隐藏的恐惧。就算不眠不休亦无济于事，因为祸乱之源会用他不停滴落的黑色血液把敌人困在噩梦中。只要祸乱之源一出现，所有英雄心中都会想起那可怖的黑暗。","stats":"<img src=\"Int\" alt=\"Intelligence\" />Intelligence:22 + 2.10<br /><img src=\"Agi\" alt=\"Agility\" />Agility:22 + 2.10<br /><img src=\"Str\" alt=\"Strength\" />Strength:22 + 2.10<br /><img src=\"Attack\" alt=\"Damage\" />Damage:33 - 39<br /><img src=\"Speed\" alt=\"Movespeed\" />Movespeed:315<br /><img src=\"Defense\" alt=\"Armor\" />Armor:4.08","stats1":[["Int","Intelligence","22 + 2.10"],["Agi","Agility","22 + 2.10"],["Str","Strength","22 + 2.10"],["Attack","Damage","33 - 39"],["Speed","Movespeed","315"],["Defense","Armor","4.08"]],"detailstats":"<div class=\"redboxContent\"><div class=\"redboxTop\"></div><div id=\"statsInner\"><div id=\"statsLeft\"><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol\">25</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">15</div><div class=\"statRowCol\">1</div>等级</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,906</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,127</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">568</div>生命值</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">1,201</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">668</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">286</div>魔法值</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">125-131</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">84-90</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">55-61</div>攻击力</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowColW\">14</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">8</div><div class=\"statRowColW\">4</div>护甲</div></div><div id=\"statsRight\"><div class=\"statRow\"></div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">1800 / 800</div>视野范围</div><div class=\"statRow\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">400</div>攻击范围</div><div class=\"statRowB\"><div class=\"statRowCol2W\">900</div>弹道速度</div></div><br clear=\"both\" /></div><div class=\"redboxBottom\"></div></div>","detailstats1":[["生命值","1,906","1,127","568"],["魔法值","1,201","668","286"],["攻击力","125-131","84-90","55-61"],["护甲","14","8","4"]],"detailstats2":[["视野范围","1800 / 800"],["攻击范围","400"],["弹道速度","900"]],"abilities":[{"key_name":"bane_enfeeble","dname":"虚弱","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">单位目标</span><br />影响：<span class=\"attribVal\">敌方单位</span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\">否</span>","desc":"虚弱一个敌方单位，降低它的物理攻击力。持续20秒。","dmg":"","notes":"虚弱无法被净化。","attrib":"攻击力削弱： <span class=\"attribVal\">30 / 60 / 90 / 120</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:95/105/115/125<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:10","lore":"即使是最强大的战士，在阿特洛波斯的恐怖面前也会崩溃。","hurl":"Bane"},{"key_name":"bane_brain_sap","dname":"蚀脑","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">单位目标</span><br />影响：<span class=\"attribVal\">敌方单位</span><br />伤害类型：<span class=\"attribVal\"><font color=\"#d61107\">纯粹</font></span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\">否</span>","desc":"暴食一个敌方单位的生命能量，造成伤害并回复自身生命值。","dmg":"攻击力:<span class=\"attribVal\">90 / 160 / 230 / 300</span>","notes":"","attrib":"生命回复量： <span class=\"attribVal\">90 / 160 / 230 / 300</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=\"魔法消耗\" />魔法消耗:100/125/150/175<br /><img src=\"cooldown\" alt=\"冷却时间\" />冷却时间:14","lore":"阿特洛波斯认为收割被他亲自制造的恐惧弄崩溃的生命是至高的享受。","hurl":"Bane"},{"key_name":"bane_nightmare","dname":"噩梦","affects":"技能：<span class=\"attribVal\">单位目标</span><br />影响：<span class=\"attribVal\">英雄</span><br />伤害类型：<span class=\"attribVal\"><font color=\"#d61107\">纯粹</font></span><br />无视技能免疫：<span class=\"attribVal\">否</span>","desc":"让目标敌方或友方英雄进入沉睡并每秒造成伤害。睡着的单位受到攻击便会醒来，但噩梦将转移到攻击者身上。噩梦中的单位受到伤害便会醒来。","dmg":"攻击力:<span class=\"attribVal\">20 / 20 / 20 / 20</span>","notes":"噩梦会对队友和自身造成伤害，所以可以用于反补英雄或自身。<br />除了噩梦造成的伤害，其他伤害都会让单位醒过来，但是只有物理攻击会使噩梦转移目标。<br />在噩梦的第一秒，作用单位是无敌状态。<br />祸乱之源可以把自己从噩梦中唤醒。","attrib":"持续时间： <span class=\"attribVal\">4 / 5 / 6 / 7</span><br />\n施法距离： <span class=\"attribVal\">500 / 550 / 600 / 650</span>","cmb":"<img src=\"mana\" alt=